2011-07-08T08:30:44Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-08/xander-co-ltd-june-sales-fall-13-34-table-6118-tt.html
XANDER CO LTD said unconsolidated sales
in June fell 13.34% to NT$675,727,000 from NT$779,706,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2011           6/2010
Sales            675,727          779,706    
YOY%             -13.34%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           4,054,875        4,692,950   
YOY%             -13.60% 
=================================================================
 